{"tid":235793,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今日係連登最撚右派既一日 犯法就要拉 冇錢就要死","createTime":"2017-05-09T09:12:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-09T09:52:39.000Z","uid":29270,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"97e15289b2c2c4204f082cd4fdc52b03a630c341","tid":235793,"uid":29270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T09:12:10.000Z","msg":"HA犯法就要被人拉 接受法律制裁<br />\n<br />\n政府打壓創作、選擇性執法、拉音樂人唔拉中國蝗、大媽跳舞冇人理玩音樂就要拉、工廈政策法律過時、娛樂牌難批、多元產業重要性、娛樂對市民既重要<br />\n<br />\n全部唔撚理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我又唔聽歌 唔聽band 唔聽live 你死關我Q事? 事不關已已不勞心<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n <br />\n <br />\nHA比唔起錢租商廈 去工廈就抵被人搞<br />\n<br />\n高地價政策、官商勾結、鋪租貴、法律不利租戶、業主想點就點、活化工廈政策失敗、工廈政策法律過時、政府保護既得利益者<br />\n<br />\n全部唔撚理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n總知冇錢就你死你事 最好取消埋綜援、生果金 冇錢就你問題 窮人生死關人忍事<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n他日有第二次佔中、第二次魚蛋革命、第三次公民廣場之戰、第N次龍和道血戰<br />\n<br />\n連登勢成支持政府最堅定之地<br />\n <br />\n犯法就要拉 冇錢就要死 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n保護弱勢？多元產業？扶助創業？創意產業？<br />\n咩黎架？食得架？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4b2d7064ddf01da72213929c596593f60cb3e65","tid":235793,"uid":29270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T09:14:02.000Z","msg":"犯法就要拉 冇錢就要死 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n政府惡法？社會不公？<br />\nWFC<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ecdce308cf0f80452bd3632c22ce261bd9f71d0","tid":235793,"uid":29270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T09:15:59.000Z","msg":"成個連登變晒藍屍大本營咁<br />\n<br 